{"tid":1757890,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"除左幫手足外，仲有d人我地係要幫","createTime":"2019-11-26T18:06:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-26T18:47:40.000Z","uid":119767,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"8d975ad19d207d52f6087c3db5a7d6c6ace452a6","tid":1757890,"uid":119767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T18:06:43.000Z","msg":"就係落敗左嘅素人<br />\n如果佢地真係有心想捲土重來嘅<br />\n希望隔離區嘅議員可以伸出援手<br />\n請佢地做議員助理<br />\n比佢地有機會多d落區去接觸市民<br />\n下次再選起碼比人睇到佢係有心做野<br />\n而且係附近嘅區做唔會比人感覺係空降<br />\n人地都會知你係邊個<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2e8a0ea0523be2986a1d6cedf5cecf876bb3d02","tid":1757890,"uid":146535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T18:07:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8071ea79f01aab896ba6a1751e9918a2ffdb4f17","tid":1757890,"uid":193371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T18:08:34.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"94c5eedbc679ad9713e97b5aa1c74b063dc54e01","tid":1757890,"uid":302963,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T18:10:44.000Z","msg":"有道理"},{"pid":"7cb84cc5b5a3c7e4bc488435163de5fd1bb0287a","tid":1757890,"uid":299490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T18:12:33.000Z","msg":"「文宣」最新香港人日程表!!!!!!<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1757860\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1757860</a>"},{"pid":"a89a7a64bc10d425aa43a6b8cd0270a0a25de780","tid":1757890,"uid":299490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T18:12:48.000Z","msg":"推，唔yuk"},{"pid":"953c6c09ae8043f3fbe3701a7b5d8441a21ad42b","tid":1757890,"uid":119767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T18:15:07.000Z","msg":"推到比議員睇到"},{"pid":"97e178d8eee5785022e3782b0076e03e598a8c49","tid":1757890,"uid":146535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T18:43:41.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"85352b61a2787feb102c8a268f661d9ff